related_items.title: Pêche aux sardines
description: Title from La production cinématographique des frères Lumière. English language release title from Rittaud-Hutinet, J. Auguste et Louis Lumière, les 1000 premiers films. Men in fishing boats off the coast of France near Marseille remove sardines from fishing nets. Catalogue Lumière no. 70. On one reel/videocassette with 58 other Lumière shorts. Second of three films on digital file. Preceded by Embarquement d'un cheval. Followed by Embarquement des filets de pêche. Filmed in Marseille. Digital files viewed. Sources used: La production cinématographique des frères Lumière, p. 217; Sadoul, G. Louis Lumière; M/B/RS Subjects files (Lumière, Louis file); M/B/RS Acquisition files (Cinémathèque française file). Available also through the Library of Congress Web site as digital files. Received: 5/22/1970; viewing print; exchange; Cinémathèque française Collection. Received: 1/24/2007 from VidiPax; master; preservation; Cinémathèque française Collection.
